                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18391021-2936-offence-1 t18391021-cd-211"></join>24th of August</rs>, 4 half-crowns, 28 shillings, and 4 sixpences, the monies of <persName id="t18391021-name-1207" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-1207" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391021-name-1207" type="surname" value="STEWARD"></interp>
